703822f-b.title: Brooklyn: Cortelyou Road - 23rd Street (East)
703822f-b.text:
Cortelyou Road, (once known as Canarsie lLane), at the N.W. corner
of East 23rd Street, showing a view of S. Cortelyou house, after it was
remodeled. The long side of house faces Cortelyou Road. It ohce stood
at 1249 Flatbush Ave.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, another view.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
